<h1 class="h1">Your workbook is ready.</h1>
<p class="body">Thanks for purchasing the Gym Startup Budget Workbook, PRO Edition. Your download link is below, and Stripe is also emailing you a receipt with a permanent link in case you need to re-access the file later.</p>

<div class="dl-card" id="dl-card">
<div class="dl-loading" id="dl-loading">Verifying purchase…</div>
<div id="dl-ready" style="display:none;">
<div class="dl-headline">Gym Startup Budget Workbook, PRO v1</div>
<div class="dl-sub">XLSX · 12 sheets · 78 formulas · single-user license</div>
<a href="#" id="dl-link" class="btn-p" download>Download the workbook &darr;</a>
</div>
<div class="dl-error" id="dl-error" style="display:none;"></div>
</div>

<h2 class="h2">A quick note before you open it</h2>
<p class="body">Start in the <strong>Format & Scenario</strong> sheet. Pick your gym format, location tier, and planning scenario. Every other sheet adapts to those inputs. Every cell in blue bold is a user input, change them to match your actual numbers. Black text is computed via formulas and updates automatically.</p>
<p class="body">If you want to walk through your specific build with someone who's done this work across multiple gym formats, <a href="/contact" style="color:#00C853;">book a 30-min intro</a>. The PRO Edition is the do-it-yourself version; the Treetop fractional engagement is the do-it-with-you version.</p>

<h2 class="h2">If you have any trouble</h2>
<ul class="ul">
<li><strong>Download link not appearing?</strong> Refresh this page once. If it still doesn't load, email <a href="mailto:bill@treetopgrowthstrategy.com" style="color:#00C853;">bill@treetopgrowthstrategy.com</a> with the order receipt, we'll send the file manually within a few hours.</li>
<li><strong>File won't open?</strong> The XLSX works in Excel, Google Sheets, and Apple Numbers. If you're seeing issues, email and we'll troubleshoot.</li>
<li><strong>Need a refund?</strong> 14 days, no questions asked. Just email.</li>
</ul>

</div></section>

<script is:inline>
(async function(){
  var params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
  var sid = params.get('session_id');
  var loading = document.getElementById('dl-loading');
  var ready = document.getElementById('dl-ready');
  var error = document.getElementById('dl-error');
  var link = document.getElementById('dl-link');

  if (!sid) {
    loading.style.display = 'none';
    error.style.display = 'block';
    error.innerHTML = 'No purchase session found. If you completed checkout but landed here, email <a href="mailto:bill@treetopgrowthstrategy.com" style="color:#00C853;">bill@treetopgrowthstrategy.com</a> with your Stripe receipt and we will send the file manually.';
    return;
  }

  try {
    var res = await fetch('/api/verify-purchase?session_id=' + encodeURIComponent(sid));
    if (!res.ok) {
      var errData = await res.json().catch(function(){return {};});
      throw new Error(errData.error || ('Verification failed: ' + res.status));
    }
    var data = await res.json();
    if (data.ok && data.download_url) {
      link.href = data.download_url;
      loading.style.display = 'none';
      ready.style.display = 'block';
    } else {
      throw new Error(data.error || 'No download URL returned');
    }
  } catch (e) {
    loading.style.display = 'none';
    error.style.display = 'block';
    error.innerHTML = 'We could not verify your purchase automatically: ' + (e.message || 'unknown error') + '. Please email <a href="mailto:bill@treetopgrowthstrategy.com" style="color:#00C853;">bill@treetopgrowthstrategy.com</a> with your Stripe receipt and we will send the file manually within a few hours.';
  }
})();
</script>

